<h2 class="bold font-l">TTYD levels</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Levels impact HP, FP, and BP. Whenever Mario gets enough Star Points, he levels up and chooses one of the three to change. </p>
</div>
</div>
